ns4:Work.dc:title: ADR pictogram 7a-Radioactive

ns4:Agent.dc:title: United Nations Economic Commision for Europe

ns4:Work.dc:description: Official ADR pictogram (formally, the European Agreement concerning the International Carriage of Dangerous Goods by Road (ADR)) is a 1957 United Nations treaty that governs transnational transport of hazardous materials.
